snippet: Karl Lagerfeld, Anna Wintour and Gisele Bündchen screen Chanel No. 5 film by Baz Luhrmann.
abstract: Matthew Schneier Front Row column describes party for Chanel No 5 ad film, directed by Baz Luhrmann and starring world-famous model Gisele Bundchen, in West Chelsea neighborhood of Manhattan.
lead_paragraph: Karl Lagerfeld, Anna Wintour and Gisele Bündchen screen Chanel No. 5 film by Baz Luhrmann.
